==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unprizable
<hw>Un*priz"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
prized or valued; being without value.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Invaluable; being beyond estimation.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unprobably</ent>⟦br⟧
